17:19.618 --> 17:28.506
They'd rather the job with the cash, with the boyfriend, and just simply go on that track because this over here is too, you know, up in the air.

17:30.929 --> 17:33.671
But man, it's far more sustainable.

17:34.932 --> 17:38.015
