17:42.159 --> 17:44.582
This is what He's doing in me and this is what He's doing through me.

17:46.143 --> 17:49.266
And I don't have to answer your expectations of me.

17:49.762 --> 17:53.366
I don't have to file the track that everybody else is following in my culture.

17:53.767 --> 17:57.812
I'm downloading from somewhere else and it's far more sustainable.

17:58.853 --> 18:10.227
Because while they're freaking out because they haven't met this deadline and this timeline and they're not married yet or they don't have kids yet or they don't have the house with the picket fence yet or whatever it is, the timeline that they're supposed to be on.

18:10.247 --> 18:11.549
Well, they're freaking out about that.

18:11.569 --> 18:13.431
I'm over here just growing.

18:14.692 --> 18:16.535
I'm over here just being fruitful.

18:17.115 --> 18:19.218
I'm over here sustainable.

18:19.362 --> 18:23.909
