18:23.929 --> 18:30.138
And so I want to give you just four keys, and I don't think we have it on the screen, but four keys to the Christian's sustainability.

18:30.358 --> 18:32.261
The first one is daily Bible reading.

18:33.803 --> 18:39.451
Daily Bible reading is a key to the sustainability of your walk with Christ.

18:40.533 --> 18:46.642
If you don't have a practice, a rhythm of reading the Bible on your own,

