01:02:07.892 --> 01:02:09.655
This is a great birthday, Jonathan says.

01:02:09.715 --> 01:02:10.195
Awesome.

01:02:10.436 --> 01:02:11.297
All right, let's go.

01:02:12.078 --> 01:02:12.499
