A couple of weeks will be my birthday.

01:02:14.902 --> 01:02:16.244
It'll be even better.

01:02:16.745 --> 01:02:17.165
Even better.

01:02:18.207 --> 01:02:19.288
Going from glory to glory.

01:02:20.650 --> 01:02:22.613
Those watching from home, God bless you.

01:02:22.673 --> 01:02:23.634
